{abstract, "Erlguten is written purely in Erlang and implements microtypographic techniques "
 "(such as margin kerning, optical alignment of margins, merning and tracking adjustments to text). "
 "It also contains a PDF rendering library as well as a Docbook Light library. "
 "Although it is still in development, it is in production use."}.
